Problem 1: Sum of Array Elements
Question: Find the sum of elements in an array.
Answer / Explanation: Each element of the array is added using a loop.
class ArraySum { public static void main(String[] args) { int[] arr = {1,2,3,4};
int sum = 0; for(int x : arr) sum += x; System.out.println(sum); } }
Problem 2: Largest Element in Array
Question: Find the largest element in an array.
Answer / Explanation: The program checks each element and stores the maximum value.
class LargestArray { public static void main(String[] args) { int[] arr =
{3,7,2,9}; int max = arr[0]; for(int x : arr) if(x > max) max = x;
System.out.println(max); } }